 <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal sm:text-xl">Bighorn Threads embroiders custom logos on workwear for Las Vegas construction crews — polos, jackets, caps, hi-vis, and FR shirts (with FR-safe Nomex thread that preserves the rating). There's no minimum on embroidery, digitizing is a one-time setup, and your stitch file is kept on record for instant reorders. Rush options available on most jobs.</p>
 </aside>
