 <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal sm:text-4xl">Embroidery is priced by stitch count.</h2>
 <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ash">
 Bigger or denser logos take more thread + more machine time. Most company marks fall under 7,000 stitches.
 </p>
 </div>

 <div class="overflow-hidden border border-hairline bg-panel">
